§7§oBoth wires and framed wires have insulated counterparts.

Insulated wires of the same color will connect to each other.

Insulated wires of different colors will not connect, letting you run multiple redstone lines in compact spaces.

Insulated wires cannot receive redstone directly, you will need a regular red alloy wire to attach to machines or levers.

For even more compactness, use bundled wires!
